# R Markdown sentence formatting

- Each sentence starts on its own line.
- Paragraphs are separated by a blank line.

```markdown
<!-- ✅ GOOD -->
This is the first sentence of a paragraph.
Here is a second sentence on a new line.

This is a new paragraph after the blank line.
Another sentence in the same paragraph.

<!-- ❌ BAD -->
This is the first sentence. Here is a second sentence on the same line.
This is a new paragraph without a blank line separating it.
```
